5. README.md
markdown# Geordie Nation 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿

## 🌟 Project Vision
Geordie Nation is a revolutionary platform designed to connect, empower, and showcase the vibrant business community of Newcastle upon Tyne and the Northeast of England.

### 🚀 Live Demo
Visit: [Your Netlify URL will go here]

### 📱 Features
- ✅ User Registration & Login
- ✅ Business Owner Accounts
- ✅ Secure Authentication
- ✅ Trust Scoring System
- ✅ Newcastle-focused Community

### 🛠️ Quick Start
1. Clone this repository
2. Run `npm install`
3. Run `npm start`
4. Open http://localhost:3000

### 📞 Contact
- Creator: Paul Gallant
- YouTube: Paul Gallant 3675
- Location: Newcastle upon Tyne, UK

### 🌐 Domain
- Target: www.geordie-nation.co.uk

---
*Powering the future of Northeast England's digital economy*
Easy Steps to Update Your GitHub:

Go to your GitHub repository: https://github.com/Paulgallant/Geordie-paul
Delete existing files (or create new ones)
Copy each file above into your repository
For the App.js file, use the complete React code from our previous conversation

Quick Deploy Commands:
Once you have these files in your repo:
bashgit add .
git commit -m "Complete Geordie Nation registration system"
git push origin main
Netlify Deploy:

Go to netlify.com
"New site from Git"
Connect your GitHub repo
Deploy!

